---
import Page from "../layouts/Page.astro";
const pageTitle = "Referencias";
---

<Page title={pageTitle}>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-10 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-800 mb-10 text-center tracking-wide">
      📚 Referencias bibliográficas
    </h1>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="p-5 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
        <p class="text-neutral-800 leading-relaxed">
          <strong>FAO</strong>. (2022). <em>El estado mundial de la agricultura y la alimentación.</em>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-5 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
        <p class="text-neutral-800 leading-relaxed">
          <strong>Bonilla, V. V., & López, D. F.</strong> (2015). <em>Evaluación de huella hídrica en cultivo de papa R12.</em>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-5 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
        <p class="text-neutral-800 leading-relaxed">
          <strong>Martín Arroyo, M.</strong> (2017). <em>El riego inteligente en la agricultura.</em> iAgua.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-5 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
        <p class="text-neutral-800 leading-relaxed">
          <strong>Colorado State University Extension.</strong> (2023). <em>Irrigation Scheduling: Principles and Practices.</em>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-5 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
        <p class="text-neutral-800 leading-relaxed">
          <strong>Li, S., Zhang, Y., & Wang, L.</strong> (2022). <em>Smart Irrigation and Precision Agriculture.</em>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 text-center text-sm text-neutral-600 italic">
      🌾 “El conocimiento florece cuando se comparte.”
    </div>
  </section>
</Page>
